<section class="how section" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="how__header">
      <h2>Operational in 72 Hours.<br/>No Disruption. No Complexity.</h2>
      <p class="how__intro">Atlas Merlin is computer vision out of the box.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="how__steps">

      <div class="how__step">
        <span class="how__step-number">01</span>
        <div class="how__step-content">
          <h3>Rugged, purpose-built hardware</h3>
          <p>IP67-rated, vibration-resistant compute units designed for the harshest environments on the planet. Paired with industrial cameras and, where needed, in-cab speakers for operator alerts. LTE and GPS connectivity built in.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="how__step">
        <span class="how__step-number">02</span>
        <div class="how__step-content">
          <h3>Installed during a standard maintenance window</h3>
          <p>No extended downtime, no special infrastructure. Your maintenance team installs the hardware and points the camera at the target. Atlas Merlin validates positioning — remotely or on-site, your preference.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="how__step">
        <span class="how__step-number">03</span>
        <div class="how__step-content">
          <h3>Calibrated and live within days</h3>
          <p>From installation to operational alerts, typically under 72 hours. A short calibration window, and the system is running.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="how__step">
        <span class="how__step-number">04</span>
        <div class="how__step-content">
          <h3>You decide who knows what, and when</h3>
          <p>Alerts go where you need them — audible in-cab, WhatsApp, Slack, Teams, email, or through the Atlas Merlin web portal. Daily summaries, real-time alerts, or both. You define the rules, or we set them up for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="how__step">
        <span class="how__step-number">05</span>
        <div class="how__step-content">
          <h3>Full visibility through one portal</h3>
          <p>Every deployed unit, every detection, system health, uptime, and alerts — visible in one place. Or let Atlas Merlin monitor it for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="how__image">
      <div class="how__placeholder">
        <p class="how__placeholder-label">Step-by-step visual: hardware arrives → installed during maintenance window → camera validated → system live and alerting. Or a product shot of the Syslogic Jetson unit and camera in an industrial setting.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how {
    background-color: var(--bg);
  }

  /* ---- Header ---- */
  .how__header {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .how__header h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .how__intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--heading);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ---- Steps ---- */
  .how__steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .how__step {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* Remove left border on first column */
  .how__step:nth-child(odd) {
    border-left: none;
  }

  /* Remove top border on first two items */
  .how__step:nth-child(1),
  .how__step:nth-child(2) {
    border-top: none;
  }

  /* Last item spans full width if odd number */
  .how__step:last-child:nth-child(odd) {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    border-left: none;
  }

  .how__step-number {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--electric-orange);
    opacity: 0.35;
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding-top: 0.1rem;
  }

  .how__step-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .how__step-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  /* ---- Image placeholder ---- */
  .how__image {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .how__placeholder {
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 6;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: var(--border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    padding: var(--space-sm);
    position: relative;
  }

  .how__placeholder::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 10px;
    border: 1px dashed var(--nav-text);
    opacity: 0.2;
  }

  .how__placeholder-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text);
    opacity: 0.5;
    max-width: 100%;
    line-height: 1.5;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* ---- Responsive ---- */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .how__steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .how__step {
      border-left: none;
    }

    .how__step:nth-child(1) {
      border-top: none;
    }

    .how__step:nth-child(2) {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .how__step:last-child:nth-child(odd) {
      grid-column: 1;
    }

    .how__placeholder {
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    }
  }
</style>
